{"tid":602062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉偷拍警嫂裙底春　休班警長被控下周提堂","createTime":"2018-03-22T17:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T04:20:10.000Z","uid":5195,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7f2d64ec70cd321bd77f0bb23be4cc74016449b8","tid":602062,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:28:10.000Z","msg":"涉偷拍警嫂的休班警被落案控告。一名丈夫任職警務人員的34歲女子，於去年11月27日在油塘大本型商場扶手電梯，遭人偷拍裙底春，警方到場拘捕一名姓莊（45歲）休班警長，莊今日已被落案控以一項「作出有違公德的行為」罪，案件將於下周四（29日）在觀塘裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"e105e0c7340a46e7d02725fcb75398266672cf86","tid":602062,"uid":4525,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"你無做錯"},{"pid":"630fcee006b71519c1efa7367c0aeba87cc8f88e","tid":602062,"uid":34461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:44:04.000Z","msg":"啊sir 影嘢唔洗你教"},{"pid":"5d154f9bd0acc3193377bbb30de9a119b1b7f117","tid":602062,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:01:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>好</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4e47cb36fce0e301d5e8505c7307036109db90e0","tid":602062,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:03:44.000Z","msg":"兄弟重要定女人重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0378c50a4dfcc29fc51b1b405e5a149f277bc9","tid":602062,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4e47cb36fce0e301d5e8505c7307036109db90e0","tid":602062,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:03:44.000Z","msg":"兄弟重要定女人重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T18:21:37.000Z","msg":"兄弟嘅女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b183a72bdab479bc7219228fa05d72ba7744d7b5","tid":602062,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc